snippet.title: EverQuest II Tears of Veeshan Expansion [OFFICIAL TRAILER]
snippet.description: Introducing EverQuest II's 10th Expansion - Tears of Veeshan!  You can now experience the Dragon Overland Realm, Channeler Class, 9 new Dungeons, and much more!  Get yours now at https://www.everquest2.com/expansion-content
